      <h3>Standards Are Not Aspirational</h3>
      <p>We do not reference ISO standards as marketing language. Each standard listed above has a direct mapping to a documented procedure in our analytical workflow. Our detection pipeline, from sample extraction through to Certificate of Analysis, is designed so that every step can be audited against these frameworks.</p>
